      "beat_id": "B06",
      "t_start": 33.0,
      "estimated_duration_s": 8.0,
      "narration_text": "Connecting a service usually grants the whole account, not the folder you had in mind. Anything the connector can read can become source material. The gap between the scope you intended and the scope you granted is exactly the material that shows up where it shouldn't.",
